  "title": "In Guará I-DF, a man spotted an oval UFO flying over Brasília-DF [1979]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/15/in-guara-i-df-a-man-spotted-an-oval-ufo-flying-over-brasilia-df-1979/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1Ge",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Brasília,<strong> November 21st, 1979</strong>. Time: 5:58 am. Duration: 15 seconds. A Post Office worker, living in Guará I, Distrito Federal, reported &#8220;the passage of an unidentified object&#8221; of oval shape and &#8220;silver color, as if it were made of stainless steel&#8221;. According to the witness, the UFO &#8220;did not emit light because its color was quite defined by the blue contrast of the sky&#8221;. Also according to the description, the UFO made no noise and was seen on a trajectory from Guará I until the Brasília Airport.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.194. “Carta sobre avistamento de objeto voador não identificado na região de Guará I, Distrito Federal, contendo desenho do trajeto do dito objeto</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
